#. Setting: Enable TDP Controls
#. Field: hint
msgid ""
"Enables TDP management by Handheld Daemon. While enabled, Handheld Daemon "
"will set and maintain the TDP limits set on start-up and during other device "
"changes (ac/dc)."
msgstr ""

